data.description: This 3 bed / 2 bath ranch home is situated on a quiet dead end street with convenient highway access. You are welcomed into the open style living room featuring original hardwood flooring that carries throughout most of the main level. Kitchen offers cherry wood cabinetry and laminate countertops. Three generously sized bedrooms and full bath on the main level. Walk-out basement is partially finished with a rec room, wood burning fireplace, second full bath & bonus room for storage plus laundry. Head out back to the expansive fenced backyard, a perfect spot to entertain family and friends. Updated architectural roof and HVAC system. Schedule your private tour today!
